## §7. QUY TẮC ĐẶT TÊN FILE (R01–R13)

**R01** — Entity memory file: `<entity>mf_<v>.json` → `<entity>khương<semver>.kris`
**R01** — Entity state file: `<entity>fs_<v>.json` → `<entity>thịnh<semver>.phieu`
**R02** — Cell manifest & boundary: `cell.manifest.json` → `<cell>.cell.anc` ; `boundary.policy.json` → `<cell>.boundary.si`
**R03** — Session file: `SES-<ulid>.json` → `SES-<ulid>.thuo`
**R04** — Self-introspection: `<entity>self.md` → `<entity>self<semver>.kris`
**R05** — Hiến Pháp: `HIEN-PHAP*.md` → `HIEN-PHAP*.anc` ; `amendments/*.md` → `amendments/*.anc`
**R06** — Contract lock: `*.contracts.lock.json` → `*.contracts.lock.si`
**R07** — Audit log: `audit-log.jsonl` → `audit-log.heyna`
**R08** — Registry: `*registry*.json` → `*registry*.sira`
**R09** — Code files giữ nguyên `.ts`, `.tsx`, `.js`, `.json`, `.png`, `.sh` (industry standard)
**R10** — Governance state: `builder-audit-trail.json` → `builder-audit-trail.heyna` ; `builder-authority-lock.json` → `builder-authority-lock.si` ; `system-state.json` → `system-state.phieu`
**R11** — Session summaries & reports: `SESSION_*.md`, `session_summary_*.md`, `*-report.json`, `*_auto.md` → `.kris`
**R12** — Bối Bối files: `boiboi_what_to_do.json` → `.phieu` ; `bmf.json`, `boiboi_memory*.json`, `boiboi_quick*.json` → `.kris`
**R13** — Entity memory files viết hoa: `THIÊN MEMORY.json`, `KIM MEMORY.json`, … → `<entity>khương.kris` ; `THIEN NHẮN *.txt` → `.heyna`

